  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Journey's Legend</h2>Are you ready to overcome the forces of evil or will the overcome you?<br>Journey's Legend is a rogue-lite game so you die, a lot.<br>Fight, Kill, Upgrade, Repeat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654080/extras/9a8185cd9cafba0c588e60db1f80fdcd.apng?t=1724865856\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654080/extras/9a8185cd9cafba0c588e60db1f80fdcd.poster.avif?t=1724865856\" class=\"bb_img\" width=384 height=128 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Choose one of 5 characters to crush your enemies  </h2>Each character comes with 4 powerful abilities and one ultimate which<br>can be unleashed after killing a certain amount of enemies. Upgrade your<br>character and its ablities to defeat the evil forces.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654080/extras/26d886d9863f85f24f7cfb8f80169c70.poster.avif?t=1724865856\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654080/extras/26d886d9863f85f24f7cfb8f80169c70.webm?t=1724865856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Unlocked powerful relics  </h2>Each character comes with 4 relic slots. Find over 30 relics to find the best combination. <br>Find even more powerful versions of the relics to completly overwhelm the enemy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654080/extras/5e2865a8307ac2488253e0ba133d74f4.apng?t=1724865856\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654080/extras/5e2865a8307ac2488253e0ba133d74f4.poster.avif?t=1724865856\" class=